children.text: AiTmed medical search engine is designed for you to find the right provider to take care of your healthcare needs
Search for doctors by symptoms, location, dates, and insurance plan
Manage your appointments and see your specialist in the most convenient way possible
Build your own healthcare network with all of your healthcare professionals
Share your professional profile and availability to leverage our healthcare e-referral platform
Come be a part of our new and improved medical practice marketing, reputation management, and patient e-referral program
Reach more providers with AiTmed search to best accommodate all of your patient’s healthcare needs
Deliver the highest quality care by improving the coordination between the patient and specialist
Maximize the power of AiTmed’s ecosystem with advanced schedule management and patient-provider-organization communication tools
Our Blockchain Technology Secures Documentation Exchange Between Facilities

Never let a referral get lost again. AiTmed’s Search & E-Referral platform secures data, making the medical documentation exchange from patient to provider the most convenient, and breaking the barriers of healthcare organizations.
